data.description: STOP PAYING RENT!!  And invest in your own beautiful top floor, end unit in the much desired Deer Run Community!  Open concept Ranch style unit with plenty of large windows for plenty of light and sunshine.  Large Living/Dining Room combo features newer flooring.  Galley style kitchen offers a large pantry closet and a pass through to the living space.  Primary bedroom suite features a full bath and large walk-in closet.  Second bedroom is a good size as well as the Laundry Room.  Additional features are a newer CA unit and an extra large 3 car tandem garage for plenty of storage.   Complex amenities include pool, tennis and clubhouse.  Ideal commuter location close to highways, bus, shopping, dining and medical facilities. Schedule your showing today!
